 139.9919, 138.4079, 138.4469, 139.1612, 139.4515, 139.298, 138.9055, 139.9326, 140.1421, 141.1501, 141.3667, 142.3231, 142.5681, 141.0021, 140.3602, 139.4376, 139.2821, 139.6498, 140.4244, 140.426, 142.137, 142.3862, 142.3489, 142.4378, 143.2702, 144.3993, 142.913, 144.0898, 144.8888, 145.6486, 145.1822, 145.5942, 147.949, 145.1703, 146.5712, 147.4629, 145.3984, 146.5686, 147.3087, 147.0492, 150.2879, 149.4094, 148.7941, 148.3878, 147.9219, 146.8269, 146.3846, 145.9219, 144.533, 142.9958, 145.7431, 147.1102, 146.3441, 147.3307, 147.974, 147.6571, 147.8633, 147.8758, 146.3394, 146.785, 145.5903, 145.8778, 144.8923, 143.3315, 141.4336, 143.8869, 146.6159, 145.4871, 145.3241, 142.6173, 145.7485, 143.5294, 142.2406, 142.6969, 145.55, 145.8063, 146.337, 148.5521, 147.9355, 145.3713, 145.8588, 145.6006, 145.1794, 146.126, 145.3914, 146.2598, 146.4467, 144.8867, 146.566, 147.2998, 150.1054, 148.2445, 150.994, 149.4693, 150.4114, 151.7342, 151.6152, 152.4322, 153.3937, 153.5726, 152.0385, 151.0781, 151.9583, 153.0756, 152.914, 151.6207, 151.4917, 151.4015, 153.3788, 154.2036, 153.3914, 152.3398, 153.0047, 153.0632, 152.0396, 150.0581, 150.9634, 151.0579, 149.4907, 149.2412, 148.9498, 150.5811, 149.4345, 149.3841], "summary_html": "<h1>聪明钱因子模型的2.0版本 -- 商品期货适配</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原始研报使用分钟行情数据构造\"聪明度指标\" S = |R|/V^beta 来识别聪明钱交易（成交量累积占比前 20% 的分钟），再计算 VWAP_smart / VWAP_all 作为选股因子。改进版将 beta 从 0.5 调整到 0.1，信息比率从 1.69 提升到 3.67。</p>\n<p><strong>商品期货适配方案</strong>：使用日频 <code>memberdiff20</code>（前 20 名席位净持仓差）直接代理聪明钱定位。席位持仓数据刻画大户机构的净多空头寸变化，概念上等同于研报中\"大单聪明钱 vs 小单普通资金\"的区分。核心因子为 <code>memberdiff20</code> 的 5 日变化量（聪明钱资金流向），截面排名后做多空。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.31</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-5.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1790</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.46</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.42</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>2.2 / 0.72</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.17</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.07</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.87</span></td><td>1.22</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.52</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.34</span></td><td>0.02</td><td>0.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>48</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1786</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>41.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>原始研报公式：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">S_t = \\frac{|R_t|}{V_t^{\\beta}}, \\quad \\beta = 0.1</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">R_t</span> 为第 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 分钟涨跌幅，<span class=\"math-tex\">V_t</span> 为第 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 分钟成交量。</p>\n<p>商品期货适配（含 minyear 修复的 EMA 平滑）：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\widetilde{m}_t = \\text{EWMA}_{\\text{span}=3}(\\text{memberdiff20}_t) \\quad\\text{(因果平滑，去高频反复)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\Delta_{5} = \\widetilde{m}_{t} - \\widetilde{m}_{t-5} \\quad\\text{(原始未平滑版本: } \\text{memberdiff20}_t - \\text{memberdiff20}_{t-5}\\text{)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{CrossSectionalRank}(\\Delta_{5,i,t}) \\in [0, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = 2 \\times (\\text{rank}_{i,t} - 0.5) \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{signal}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 为品种，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{\\text{target}} = 0.12</span>，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}</span> 为 60 日滚动波动率。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>最优变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>诊断 -&gt; 行动 -&gt; 效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>combo_vt015_h20_raw</td><td>0.88</td><td>组合因子通过阈值; 底部品种AL/JD/OI/CF/AP拖累 -&gt; R2排除弱品种+拆分单因子</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>d5_ex5_vt015_h20_raw</td><td>1.19</td><td>delta5单因子+EX5排除优于组合(+35%); 新底部TA/JM/A出现 -&gt; R3扩大排除集EX8+细化vt</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>d5_ex8_vt012_h20_raw</td><td>1.50</td><td>EX8排除+降低vt=0.12进一步提升(+26%); 信号质量稳健(TS ICIR=0.39) -&gt; 达标终止</td></tr><tr><td>TIER-A</td><td>sm3d5_ex8_vt012_h20_raw</td><td>1.236</td><td>minyear缺陷(2023 -1.03&lt;-1.0): broad-whipsaw -&gt; memberdiff20先EMA(3)平滑再取delta5 -&gt; 2023 -1.03→-0.34, 整体几乎不变 -&gt; fixed</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R2发现delta5单因子(聪明钱5日资金流向)远优于三因子组合。原因是level和intensity引入了噪声，纯粹的资金流向变化信号更干净。R3通过扩大排除集和降低波动率目标进一步提升风险调整后收益。TIER-A 修复识别出 2023 年的全品种 whipsaw 是 delta 对高频噪声敏感所致，用 EMA(3) 因果平滑即可削平崩盘年而不损整体 Sharpe。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频 (使用 memberdiff20 字段)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货，排除 AL/JD/OI/CF/AP/TA/JM/A 共 8 个噪声品种</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20 日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>数据起始</strong>: memberdiff20 字段从 2018-12 开始，非空率 59%</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原始研报基于股票分钟微观结构数据，此处用日频席位持仓代理，因子构造有较大差异\n<p>- memberdiff20 字段仅覆盖约 59% 的数据点，部分品种/日期缺失 - 排除了 8 个品种，可能过拟合排除集 - hold_days 对再平衡相位较敏感（h20 稳健，h15/h25/h30 因相位错配会显著波动），实盘建议固定 h20 或做多相位平均 - 2025 年（部分样本，仅 97 个交易日）修复变体 Sharpe -0.26，样本量小不构成 minyear 触发</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>DELTA_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>5-day change of memberdiff20</td></tr><tr><td><code>EMA_SPAN</code></td><td><code>3</code></td><td>causal EMA smoothing span (sm3d5 parity variant)</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 2.11s</li>\n</ul>"}